ActCanadian International Trade Tribunal Act
PrecisApproval of the Minister’s decision to authorize JEAN BÉDARD of Ottawa, Ontario, to act as Chairperson of the Canadian International Trade Tribunal for a term of one year, effective July 1, 2016, or until a Chairperson is appointed, whichever is earlier.
